der)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/TAYLOR-SWIFT">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ED-SHEERAN">艾德·希兰</a>.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wholl-be-supporting-oasis-on-their-reunion-tour-fans-and-artists-share-theories-and-requests-3787727">对于谁可以在巡演中支持乐队也有很多猜测</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blossoms">Blossoms</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kasabian">Kasabian</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/manic-street-preachers">Manic Street Preachers</a>都被认为是可能的。</p><p>乐队尚未透露谁将与 Liam 和 Noel 一起组成完整阵容，但本周报纸报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-rumoured-to-reform-with-only-the-gallagher-brothers-and-no-other-original-members-3787367">称“预计不会有其他原 Oasis 成员加入重聚”</a> ，并且“Noel Gallagher 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">High Flying</a>成员”<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">鸟类</a>将介入音乐会”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3787542" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3787542" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3787542" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE.jpg" alt="Liam 和 Noel Gallagher 终于聚在一起，在 2025 年联合 Oasis 进行英国和爱尔兰体育场巡演。图片来源：Simon Emmett" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="